column1: #build start(15;10; Top left corner of central stairs) Placing grates, doors, and screw pumps for the fortwide waterfall plumbing.\n\nStart this blueprint from the BOTTOM of the screw pump tower (lowest Z-level), and repeat UPWARDS. Each repetition does 2 floors. Directly above the top level of plumbing you build should be the waterfall plumbing floor.
